:2080933,"uid":107212,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:22:46.000Z","msg":"呢個世界係需要少量通脹<br />\n<br />\n因為人要知佢啲錢唔用會貶值佢先會洗錢同投資<br />\n<br />\n成個經濟學根本係心理學黎"},{"pid":"acc32b186aa5acf14c27d5d66fb624e9840eb68b","tid":2080933,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d576a422b93cae60ad0df7245914d378f54aff88","tid":2080933,"uid":33059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:19:05.000Z","msg":"呢個世界無窮人會世界大亂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:35:38.000Z","msg":"儘量減少呢個數目，例如強迫有錢人生仔，唔畀窮人生"},{"pid":"2213daa455b568cb42b7cf06acc0432d1234bd65","tid":2080933,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:48:31.000Z","msg":"我都唔識經濟<br />\n不過我相信係 錢 呢種量化工具<br />\n之後先有 窮 呢種概念<br />\n<br />\n想像人類之初<br />\n你有你養牛揸下牛奶<br />\n我有我種田種菜<br />\n大家得閒就交換下生活所需<br />\n何來你窮定我窮既觀念？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7dc8c79a2d271c3337ec0ee66b245668aaab04b","tid":2080933,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2213daa455b568cb42b7cf06acc0432d1234bd65","tid":2080933,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:48:31.000Z","msg":"我都唔識經濟<br />\n不過我相信係 錢 呢種量化工具<br />\n之後先有 窮 呢種概念<br />\n<br />\n想像人類之初<br />\n你有你養牛揸下牛奶<br />\n我有我種田種菜<br />\n大家得閒就交換下生活所需<br />\n何來你窮定我窮既觀念？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:16:44.000Z","msg":"我擁有好多牛，啲牛奶多到可以賣出去換其他物品(例如雞蛋)。<br />\n你種菜就淨係夠自己食，拎咗嚟換其他物品你就唔夠菜食。"},{"pid":"3b1fc49e9674a3cd0c4cad8748d8b9925d4d9cdf","tid":2080933,"uid":74663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acc32b186aa5acf14c27d5d66fb624e9840eb68b","tid":2080933,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d576a422b93cae60ad0df7245914d378f54aff88","tid":2080933,"uid":33059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:19:05.000Z","msg":"呢個世界無窮人會世界大亂"},"citedBy":1,"r